
* k8s local development environment

cdk                  = chdir to k8s source directory
dind-up [N]          = bring up N-node DIND (Docker-in-Docker) cluster
dind-up quick [N]    = bring up N-node DIND cluster without rebuilding
                       the containers
dind-down            = bring down DIND cluster
vagrant-up           = bring up Vagrant cluster
vagrant-down         = bring down Vagrant cluster
local-up             = bring up the local cluster
use-dind             = switch to using DIND closter
use-local            = switch to 'local' provider (use with local-up)
use-vagrant          = switch to 'vagrant' provider
list_e2e             = list available e2e tests using Ginkgo dry run
e2e [focus]          = run e2e test(s) optionally filtering them
                       by name using 'focus' regexp
update-kubelet       = update kubelet on the vagrant-based nodes
testit [pkg] [regex] = run some of the unit tests
devhelp              = display this help

* native k8s commands

make               = build k8s binaries
make quick-release = build k8s release for use with kube-up
make test          = run unit tests

